      "ipa": "ɪt ˌhæzənt ˈstɑːr.ɾɪd ˌjɛt.",
      "start_ms": 91880,
      "end_ms": 92680
    },
    {
      "_id": "69199f69b41f5ecfe3202eee",
      "text": "So what are we thinking?",
      "translations": {
